product.name: Cosmic Gel Liner
product.description: Swap your standard wing for eyes that twinkle like stars! A beam of Cosmic Gel Eye Liner makes an out of this world statement through an intense burst of sparkle and bold color. Available in three shades packed with interstellar shimmer, this formula glides on silky-smooth and is super easy to blend. Like our fan fave Gel Liner and Smudger, these rich colors stay put for strong galactic glam.
